dc_description_s: This map service contains the index grids for the historic NAIP imagery. The NAIP program is administered by the U.S. Department of Agriculture Farm Service Agency and has been established to support two main FSA strategic goals centered on agricultural production.Historic NAIP Imagery Links:http://imagery.geodata.md.gov/imap/rest/services/NAIP/NAIPImagery2005/MapServerhttp://imagery.geodata.md.gov/imap/rest/services/NAIP/NAIPImagery2007/MapServerhttp://imagery.geodata.md.gov/imap/rest/services/NAIP/NAIPImagery2009/MapServerhttp://imagery.geodata.md.gov/imap/rest/services/NAIP/NAIPImagery2011/MapServerMap Service Link:http://imagery.geodata.md.gov/imap/rest/services/NAIP/HistoricNAIPImageryGrid/MapServer
